<center><h2 id="about">
HACKATHON Institute of Engineering & Technology is one of the premier industry-oriented and application-driven institutes in India. Shree HACKIT Charity Trust, under Chairmanship of renowned industrialist ANTIEKU, set up HACKIT, in 2007.

The Institution has been true to its commitment in providing quality education in Engineering and Technology. Our strong alliances with leading international universities, industries and professional bodies have increased access to latest education, opportunities for engagement and exchange, collaborative research and innovation for our students and faculties. We believe the best way to help HACKITians meet challenges is to provide a supportive and enriching environment


